name.jp: ベイビー・ポップクランク

description.en: A scary but fast, baby, Popcrank that follows its master around and picks up dropped items
description.ar: A scary but fast, baby, Popcrank that follows its master around and picks up dropped items
description.br: Um assustador e rápido, bebê, Popcrank que segue seu mestre e coleta itens no chão.
description.cns: 一只可怕但是快速的魔盒小丑宝宝跟随它的主人并捡起周围掉落的物品。
description.de: Ein furchteinflößendes aber immerhin schnelles Baby Popcrank, das seinem Meister folgt und Gegenstände aufsammelt.
description.fi: A scary but fast, baby, Popcrank that follows its master around and picks up dropped items
description.fil: A scary but fast, baby, Popcrank that follows its master around and picks up dropped items
description.fr: Fait apparaître un bébé Totemia, effrayant mais rapide, qui suit son invocateur partout et ramasse les objets laissés par les ennemis.
description.id: Menakutkan tapi cepat, sayang, Popcrank yang mengikuti tuannya berkeliling dan mengambil barang-barang yang dijatuhkan
description.it: A scary but fast, baby, Popcrank that follows its master around and picks up dropped items
description.jp: ご主人様の後をついて、落ちたものを拾う恐いけど速い赤ちゃんポップクランク
